### BUG-09: `RankTrendChart` has `connectNulls` prop — but the comment says it shouldn't

**File:** [RankTrendChart.tsx#L61](file:///c:/Users/panga/OneDrive/Desktop/Seva/SRSMA/SRSMADashBoard/src/components/RankTrendChart.tsx#L61)

